<ab facs="#facs_209_r2l15">wie etwas vehe entſtanden ſeÿ / <expan>cʒwiſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr / vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Sweick<ex>er</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r2l16"><expan>Gundolfing<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / das vns nicht lıeb ıſt / . <expan>Dar<ex>vmb</ex></expan> <expan>bıt<ex>en</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_209_r2l17">ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleiʒʒıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr vns <expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet / <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒe reden </ab>
