<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Hans und <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> und Wigleis, wir
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie etwas vehe entstanden sey
                                <expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sweick<ex>er</ex></expan> von <expan>Gundolfing<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, das uns nicht lieb ist.
                                <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleizzikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>, daz ir uns
                            <expan>günne<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        cze reden; so mainten wir ein stallung und einen
                                <expan>frewntliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag czemachen her czü uns gen
                                <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> enden, do es ew bederseit gelegenlich wer;
                        und was <add>wir</add>
<expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> gütes dar czü gereden möchten, daz das
                        abgetragen und <expan>frewntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> berichtet würd, des wern
                        wir willig und <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tün. Und lasset uns des ewr
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>dise<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.</ab>
</div>
